precondition: The text editor area with the existing text is in focus.
action: Click at the end of the existing text in the document editing area.
expected_results: A blinking text cursor will appear at the end of the existing text, allowing the user to continue typing from that point.

precondition: The "Print" dialog box is open in a word processing application.
expected_results: The print job will be sent to the printer, and the document will begin printing according to the specified settings.
